fields.faq_question: What graphic design software do you teach in your courses at Oxdu Tech?
fields.faq_answer: At Oxdu Tech, we cover industry-standard graphic design software such as Adobe Creative Suite, ensuring our students gain proficiency in tools widely used in the field.

fields.faq_question: Are the Python development courses suitable for beginners?
fields.faq_answer: Absolutely! Our Python development courses cater to all skill levels, providing comprehensive learning materials and hands-on projects to support beginners while challenging more experienced developers.

fields.faq_question: Do you offer practical experience in mobile development courses?
fields.faq_answer: Yes, our mobile development courses include practical, real-world projects that allow students to apply their skills, ensuring they are well-prepared for the challenges of mobile app development.

fields.faq_question: How does your digital marketing program stay updated with industry trends?
fields.faq_answer: Our digital marketing courses are regularly updated to reflect the latest industry trends and tools, ensuring our students receive relevant and current knowledge in areas like SEO, social media marketing, and online advertising.
